                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">Ambassador <persName type="from">Meyer</persName> to the
                            <gloss type="to">Secretary of State</gloss>
                    </hi>.</head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.—Paraphrase.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">American Embassy</hi>,<lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">St. Petersburg</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1906-02-27">
                            <hi rend="italic">February 27, 1906</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>(Mr. Meyer states that it has been officially announced that the Douma will
                    convene on the 10th of May.)</p>
            </div>
